headline: Why Chubb Limited Fell Today
summary: Chubb fell along with most of the rest of the insurance sector.  Signs of increased competition, as well as a worrying study on homeowner readiness for catastrophes may be affecting property and casualty names today.  A big decline in health insurance may also be affecting the broader sector.
